description:
Japanese title: Zetsub no Naka de Nibuku Hikaru -Jinrui no Saiki (1)- ( )

The drill instructor Shardis evaluates the new recruits and taunts them with insults. When he finds Cadet Braus, eating a boiled potato while in lineup, he makes her run around the camp until sunset without food or drink. Tensions begin between Eren who wants to fight the titans, and Jean who wants to take a cushy position in the Military Police posted in the inner city walls. The recruits train on an Omni-directional Mobility Gear (ODM) simulator, where they have to maintain balance while suspended on just two cables. Eren has trouble balancing and continually fails. The following day, Eren almost balances on the apparatus but falls again, however Shardis discovers that he was issued defective equipment, and so Eren passes.
name: A Dim Light in the Darkness of Despair: Humanity Rises Again, Part 1

name: Night of the Graduation Ceremony: Humanity Rises Again, Part 2
